@startuml UC08_Sequence
title UC08: 加入候补名单 - 顺序图

actor "学生" as StudentActor
boundary "候补确认对话框" as WaitForm
control "选课控制类" as EnrollCtrl
entity "Waitlist" as WList

StudentActor -> WaitForm : 确认加入候补
WaitForm -> EnrollCtrl : addToWaitlist(studentId, courseId)
EnrollCtrl -> WList : addEntry(studentId, courseId)
WList --> EnrollCtrl : position
EnrollCtrl --> WaitForm : 成功及排队位置
WaitForm -> StudentActor : 提示已在候补中
@enduml
